        class="service-icon"
        data-lg-reveal="fade"
        data-lg-reveal-delay=".02"
        data-lg-parallax
        data-lg-parallax-amplitude="0.4"
        data-lg-lottie="/animations/web-design.json"
        data-lg-lottie-autoplay="true"
        data-lg-lottie-loop="true"
        data-lg-lottie-lazy="true"
      >
      </div>
      <h3 data-lg-parallax>Websites</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="service-right">
      <p>
        Your website should make the next step obvious. We design and build websites, stores, and applications that
        reduce friction and turn attention into action.
      </p>
      <ul data-lg-reveal data-lg-reveal-stagger="0.1">
        <li data-lg-reveal="layer-to-right">
          <a href="/services/applications/">App Development</a>
        </li>
        <li data-lg-reveal="layer-to-right">
          <a href="/services/website-development/">Web Design</a>
        </li>
        <li data-lg-reveal="layer-to-right">
          <a href="/services/website-development/">Web Development</a>
        </li>
        <li data-lg-reveal="layer-to-right">
          <a href="/services/ecommerce/">Ecommerce</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="service service--marketing" id="marketing-strategy">
    <div class="service-left">
      <div data-lg-parallax data-lg-parallax-amplitude="0.2">
        <div class="service-square" data-lg-reveal="layer-to-right"></div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="service-icon"
        data-lg-reveal="fade"
        data-lg-reveal-delay=".02"
        data-lg-parallax
        data-lg-parallax-amplitude="0.4"
        data-lg-lottie="/animations/digital-marketing.json"
        data-lg-lottie-autoplay="true"
        data-lg-lottie-loop="true"
        data-lg-lottie-lazy="true"
      >
      </div>
      <h3 data-lg-parallax>Marketing & Strategy</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="service-right">
      <p>
        Marketing breaks down when the audience is unclear, the campaigns are disconnected, or the reporting never
        answers what to do next. We help bring strategy, execution, and measurement together.
      </p>
      <ul data-lg-reveal data-lg-reveal-stagger="0.1">
        <li data-lg-reveal="layer-to-right">
          <a href="/services/audience-targeting/">Audience Targeting</a>
        </li>
        <li data-lg-reveal="layer-to-right">
          <a href="/services/campaign-management/">Campaign Management</a>
        </li>
        <li data-lg-reveal="layer-to-right">
          <a href="/services/copywriting/">Copywriting</a>
        </li>
        <li data-lg-reveal="layer-to-right">
